        <ul><b>6. What is the correct CSS syntax to select all paragraphs on a page?</b>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio6" id="radio">a) p { }</li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio6" id="radio">b) paragraph { }</li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio6" id="radio">c) .paragraph { }</li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio6" id="radio">d) < p> { }</li></ul>
        <details><summary>Answer</summary><p>a) p { }</p></details>
    </div>

    <div>
        <ul><b>7. Which HTML tag is used to define an unordered list?</b>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio7" id="radio">a) < ul></li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio7" id="radio">b) < ol></li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio7" id="radio">c) < list></li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio7" id="radio">d) < li></li></ul>
        <details><summary>Answer</summary><p>a) < ul></p></details>
    </div>

    <div>
        <ul><b>8. Which property is used to change the font size of an element?</b>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio8" id="radio">a) font-size</li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio8" id="radio">b) text-size</li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio8" id="radio">c) size</li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio8" id="radio">d) font-style</li></ul>
        <details><summary>Answer</summary><p>a) font-size</p></details>
    </div>

    <div>
        <ul><b>9. Which CSS property is used to make text italic?</b>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio9" id="radio">a) text-style: italic;</li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio9" id="radio">b) font-style: italic;</li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio9" id="radio">c) italic: true;</li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio9" id="radio">d) style: italic;</li></ul>
        <details><summary>Answer</summary><p>b) font-style: italic;</p></details>
    </div>

    <div>
        <ul><b>10. What is the correct HTML for creating a hyperlink?</b>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio10" id="radio">a) < a href="link">Click here</a></li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio10" id="radio">b) < link href="link">Click here</link></li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio10" id="radio">c) < hyperlink>Click here</hyperlink></li>
        <li><input type="radio" name="radio10" id="radio">d) < href="link">Click here</a></li></ul>
        <details><summary>Answer</summary><p>a) < a href="link">Click here</a></p></details>
